;
A009,0,Mileage/Odometer
A009,5,Mileage/Odometer
A009,6,Increments: 1 = 10 km or 1 = 10 mi
A009,7, 
A009,8,The distance can only be changed once until
A009,9,the current value is not over 100 km/62 mi.
A009,10, 
A009,11,NOTE: Perform Login first.
;
